Step 1 Go inside backend folder -> cd backend
Step 2 Create Virtual envrionment -> python3 -m venv venv
This creates backend/
        ├── venv/
        └── app/
Step 3 Activate Virtual envrionment -> source venv/bin/activate
 Your terminal should now show something like:-->(venv) Shruti-Mac backend %
 Step 4 — Install FastAPI + Uvicorn
 pip install fastapi uvicorn 
 Then freeze dependencies: pip freeze > requirements.txt
 This Creates --> backend/requirements.txt
 git add .
git commit -m "Setup virtual environment and install FastAPI"
git push

/* -------- */ 

What You Just Learned
	•	Virtual environments
	•	Dependency management
	•	requirements.txt
	•	Isolated backend setup

These are real backend fundamentals.

